<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="453" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,153,719]" box="[199,1104,621,647]" pageId="2" pageNumber="453">
Members of the group are widespread in 
<collectingRegion box="[660,980,621,647]" isEnumeration="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="453">Gansu, Qinghai and Sichuan</collectingRegion>
provinces.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,153,719]" pageId="2" pageNumber="453">Most of known taxa are typical for meadow landscapes at high altitudes, few species inhabit the forests floor at middle elevations.</paragraph>
